ebanana.com/img/ss/mods/641630e2283d1.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/641630dde175d.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/64163239e6d95.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/641630d0b083f.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6416323ccb669.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/64163232d0e34.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6416322007081.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6416324202fd7.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/641632455d60d.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; DAR 3.3a - FREE&lt;br&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;QUICK UPDATE AND BUGFIX&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Changelog:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;+ Small Change to Hero's Fury Mechanic&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Now you gonna need always just 1 Red Star to use Hero's Fury, at any Calamity Level&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;+ New Icons for Hero's Fury&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Better Icons have been added to all Furies&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;+ New Effects for Hero's Fury activation menu&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Brand New Effects have been added in the Hero's Fury activation menu&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img src="https://c10.patreonusercontent.com/4/patreon-media/p/post/106800430/1408a1e3ce834f95916cacff2e11d5a1/e30%3D/1.gif?token-time=1720483200&amp;amp;token-hash=eaRSeH4feQsFaz6BwStDBib7441RWsjBszskTUcFvMA%3D"&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;+ Fixed some Hero's Fury&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt; Weapons&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Fixed some Hero's Fury Weapons that could be thrown, now none of Hero's Fury Weapons can be thrown&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;+ Fixed Random Stal Lynels&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Fixed Stal Lynels equipment, now they gonna have Magical or Elemental Weapons and Elemental Bows&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Thanks for supporting this project!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;ENJOY!!!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Adjustment&lt;/em&gt;: Small Change to Hero's Fury Mechanic&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Adjustment&lt;/em&gt;: New Icons for Hero's Fury&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Addition&lt;/em&gt;: New Effects for Hero's Fury activation menu&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Bugfix&lt;/em&gt;: Fixed some Hero's Fury Weapons&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Bugfix&lt;/em&gt;: Fixed Random Stal Lynels&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;If you like this mod please consider making a &lt;a href="https://paypal.me/miirkuz" target="_blank"&gt;DONATION&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&#13;
&lt;b&gt;Concept&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#13;
&lt;br&gt;Something went wrong with the ritual that awakened Link, maybe Zelda &#13;
said the wrong words, who knows, the fact is that the Dark Army has been&#13;
 awakened.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#13;
I'm Miirkuz, a mod creator for Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild with 3 years experience and &lt;strong&gt;Dark Army Resurrection&lt;/strong&gt; is my main project.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#13;
With &lt;strong&gt;more than 2 years&lt;/strong&gt; of developing and &lt;strong&gt;more than 40.000 downloads&lt;/strong&gt;, DAR has become pretty popular even because some of the most important streamers have been playing with DAR for months.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#13;
This mod add tons of unique features to the original game like a &lt;strong&gt;Skill System&lt;/strong&gt; based on collecting &lt;strong&gt;Souls&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;Random Locked Chests System&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;Random Spawning Enemies&lt;/strong&gt;, lots of &lt;strong&gt;Unique Weapons&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;Punitive Death&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;Punitive Blood Moon&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;Replayable Divine Beasts&lt;/strong&gt; and many many more.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#13;
The thing that makes this mod unique is the fact that you can &lt;strong&gt;customize&lt;/strong&gt; it using &lt;strong&gt;more than 100 options&lt;/strong&gt; and some of them are selectable in game through a &lt;strong&gt;Campfire Menu&lt;/strong&gt;!&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#13;
