This mod require a specific procedure to be installed correctly, so make sure to check &lt;a href="https://github.com/miirkuz/DarkArmyResurrection/wiki/1---Wiki-Home" target="_blank"&gt;DAR Official Wiki&lt;/a&gt; for full details.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Versions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Starting from version 3.0 the release method is gonna be different, there are gonna be 2 different versions.&#13;
I've decided to setup a Patreon Page for DAR.&#13;
