    <item>
      <title>Cemu Spawn Menu</title>
      <link>https://gamebanana.com/mods/523573</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">0f069ced7d3292951585934b4a93c98b06216200</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 00:37:14 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/667984dd0c672.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/667984ebdfdbf.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6678bf522535e.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6678bf7147bbc.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6678bf8457264.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6678bf91987ff.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6678bf9bb1e20.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;Allows to spawn some actors, to spawn some clothes, move Link in all directions ( even through walls or under water ), view Link coordinates ( in log.txt ), save and load Link position ( without reloading ).&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;How to install? Download BNP and install it in BCML.&lt;br&gt;How to enable? Load game, load save, then press A + B + Y, mod is enabled, enable message should be shown.&amp;nbsp; Only Wii U Game Pad supported ( cause it's hooked VPADRead function in asm patch, not KPADRead )&lt;br&gt;How to disable? Press again A + B + Y, mod is disabled, disabled message should be shown.&lt;br&gt;How to switch menus? Press A + STICK_L_LEFT ( left joystick to the left ) or A + STICK_L_RIGHT ( left joystick to the right ) and release. Menu name should be shown.&lt;br&gt;How to switch between items in current menu? Press A + STICK_L_UP ( left joystick up ) or A + STICK_L_DOWN ( left joystick down ). Item name should be shown.&lt;br&gt;How to activate menu item? Press X + Y. Actor or chest with clothes should be spawned, or some command executed.&lt;br&gt;What are commands? ViewLink, SaveLink, LoadLink, MoveLink, GoLink&lt;br&gt;What is ViewLink? Command posts Link coordinates in log.txt if Cemu menu Debug/Logging/Coreinit Logging is enabled&lt;br&gt;What is SaveLink? Command saves current Link coordinates in memory.&lt;br&gt;What is LoadLink? Command moves Link to coordinates saved in memory.&lt;br&gt;What is MoveLink? Command moves Link relatively to his current coordinates. For example Jump 100 moves Link 100 meters in air, Dive -10 moves Link 10 meters under ground.&lt;br&gt;What is GoLink? Command moves Link by absolute coordinates, for example to Bomb Shrine.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;So, this time almost complete port of my mod &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/tools/16866"&gt;Botw_Spawn&lt;/a&gt; for WUPS in tools section.&lt;br&gt;Why not update in &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/519830"&gt;Cemu Spawn Mod&lt;/a&gt;? Well this mod differs internally and by using. In latter mod all actors were separate submods and that break immersion cause there is need to switch from fullscreen and select different submod for different actor. Now it's just one big mod and all switching happens internally. Also this mod already contains &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/519833"&gt;Chest with Drop Tables 32&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;and &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/519834"&gt;Static Explosives&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;mods.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Is it possible to port to WiiU code patch? In theory yes, cause now it just one big mod, but memory requirements are also way bigger now, so only if there's option to increase available memory for U-King.rpx process ( exe file for BOTW )&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Is it possible to port to Switch? Very hard, cause very different architecture ( ARM vs PPC ), also Cemu and WiiU way more mature for ( homebrew ) development than Ryujinx and Switch.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;How to change menus and items? BCML copies patches to graphicPacks\bcmlPatches\SpawnMenu folder. There's patch_Spawn_Menu.js - windows javascript file, if edit that file ( menu is at the beginning ) and then run it ( in Explorer ) rules.txt and&amp;nbsp;patch_Spawn_Menu.asm would be regenerated. Remember that to reload asm patch Cemu and Botw not need to be restarted.</description>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/spawn_menu_48827.bnp" type="application/octet-stream"/>
      <category>Cemu GraphicPack</category>
      <category>Cemu GraphicPack</category>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Cemu Spawn Graphics Pack</title>
      <link>https://gamebanana.com/mods/519830</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">1f44de3dff2db7aa93f22615f6d34f641dad6f87</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 22:19:31 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66676a61e0381.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66676a6ab5bb8.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66676a72225c7.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66676a766a654.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; bnp&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Convert mod to BNP format ( whoever may need this ). Unfortunately on first load all sub mods are enabled, which is not good, that requires manual disabling each sub mod from user.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;Cemu Graphics Pack that allows to spawn some actors in game. Kinda early ( if ever ) porting of my Botw_Spawn plugin for WUPS ( see in tools section ). &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;How to install? Download ZIP archive and unpack in Cemu\graphicsPack folder ( there's should be new folder - Spawn ). &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;How to enable? Launch Cemu, goto graphics Packs menu, Spawn submenu and check some patch - for example Spawn/Weapon Sets/Arrow Packs. Select just one patch at a time.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;How to use? During gameplay press X + Y on your controller that emulated Wii U Gamepad. Arrow packs should be spawn.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;How to disable? Uncheck selected pack in menu. Works during gameplay.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;How to change what to spawn? Uncheck selected pack and check new pack, also works during gameplay.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Is it stable? Kinda buggy, cause it's big asm patch. So save often. Not tested on USA, JPN versions. Cemu version tested 2.0 - 82&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Too many submenus? Delete subfolder in Spawn folder. For example Spawn/Animals.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;How to spawn different actors? Well, try to edit PowerPC assembler in *.asm file, there's some comments when actor name loaded in registers. Kinda messy, I know.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;What's big block of binary data in the middle of the patch? It's sine and cosine table from -180 degree to 179 degree for rotation.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;It's asm patch, so possible to backport to Wii U in U-King.rpx that doesn't require WUPS? In theory yes, but in practice CEMU allow to use much more memory for patches in code caves, and my patches are very big. Also process memory layout kinda different, some how same U-King.rpx places some bytes in different locations on Wii U and Cemu. So use Botw_Spawn on HW Wii U.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Conflicts with other mods that are asm patches? Nothing that I know and to my knowledge this is first ( searched only community patches ) asm patch that hooks VPADRead to process X + Y press in game.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Require other mods? To spawn clothes in chest requires &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/519833"&gt;Chests with Drop Table 32&lt;/a&gt; mod, also to spawn explosives in shapes like square ( submenu Walls ) also requires &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/519834"&gt;Static Explosives&lt;/a&gt; mod.&lt;br&gt;</description>
