ero Set  11: Tingle's Set 12:Flamebreaker Set  13: Hylian Set  14: Zora Set  15: Rubber Set  16: Radiant Set  17: Ancient Set  18: Salvager Set  19: Hero Of Wild Set  20: Dark Set  21: Fierce Deity Set 22: Soldier's Set  23: Snowquill Set  24: Royal Guard Set&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Hylian Hood's A and B are switched depending on the upper armor.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;[ Recommended ]&lt;br&gt;When using this mod, please set the Mods / Draw Distance / Texture Distance Detail (LOD) item in the Cemu graphics pack settings to Very High (-4) or higher.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Please select one of the files below to install. Select each option in the BCML installation window.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
