anana.com/members/1705492"&gt;ShadowMarth-JTW&lt;/a&gt; for allowing me to upload this to gamebanana and creating the incredible Relics mod :D&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;If you enjoyed the mod, please consider clicking in the like button, it helps pushing the mod to more people! (and makes me happy :D)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Skywatchers and Turrets only receive damage from reflected beams (use ancient shield if skill issue)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;h1&gt;DISCLAIMER: &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;THE MOD WAS MADE BY ME, ANY ISSUES WITH IT&lt;/span&gt; (or caused by it) &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;ARE TO BE ADDRESSED WITH ME, DO NOT SPAM MARTH OR THE CALAMITY REFUGE STAFF ABOUT THIS&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;h1&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;h1&gt;DM ME HERE OR PING ME THERE FOR QUESTIONS RELATED TO THIS&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href="https://discord.gg/FEWRrhq" target="_blank"&gt;Calamity Refuge Discord server&lt;/a&gt; [Only ping me for questions about this mod, &lt;u class="SelectedElement"&gt;DO NOT PING THE STAFF OR MARTH&lt;/u&gt;&lt;u&gt;]&lt;/u&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;</description>
