      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 15:29:42 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/666326cd9cd75.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65e4d440b1180.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65e4d47f97a95.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; New Versions&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Balanced version:&lt;br&gt;1.25x Damage, 5x Durability&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Ultra Op:&lt;br&gt;2.5x Damage, 10x Durability&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Removed old UKMM zip due to it being outdated, if you want to use this mod on UKMM, install the bnp, if you encounter issues, &lt;a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://github.com/NiceneNerd/UKMM/issues"&gt;open a issue on UKMM github page&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ANY ISSUES REGARDING UKMM WILL BE DISSMISSED&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Addition&lt;/em&gt;: 2 new versions&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Removal&lt;/em&gt;: Old UKMM zip&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;This mod Increases both durability and the damage of royal guard gear, to better reflect its rarity (only 2 of each in hyrule castle) and to make them more usefull (they are weaker than savage lynel gear, something you can easily farm) if they are way too op, comment and i maybe do a less op version&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;DURABILITY STAYS THE SAME FOR WEAPONS ALREADY IN YOUR INVENTORY&lt;br&gt;(pick new ones at hyrule castle to get higher durability, or use the save editor)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Durability increased by 10x&lt;br&gt;Damage increased by 1.5x&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Tutorial I used https://gamebanana.com/tuts/13415&lt;br&gt;</description>
